HEADWORD: Excavator
<hw>Ex"ca*va`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, excavates or hollows out; a machine, as a dredging machine, or a
tool, for excavating.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

